name: Sam Dayton
text: Arrived here to get some food and they only had cheese pizzas, I will not return to this place of business period. Also I will advise my family and friends to also boycott this place. My suggestion if you want pizza go somewhere else. Poor business.

text: Beautifully built neighborhood strip mall located at 18th & I 70 highway..Sun Fresh Market is also located in this strip mall.

name: Corey McGovern
text: I stopped in for a couple quick pizzas for dinner, the staff was a little frazzled as it was unusually busy and they had some large orders go out and had some new people working the back. I had a 20 minute wait for my pizzas that would have normally been a grab and go, but the pies were fantastic and really fresh.

name: Matthue Brown
text: I don't get the whole HotnReady thing, people actually want to buy pizza that's been sitting for hours or so? Went here once, price isn't bad but you get what you pay for. And the pizza I got was not fresh by any stretch.
